window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A mysterious guest arrives at Blackwood Farm, disrupting the delicate harmony of Asher’s life.</b></p> <p>As Asher and Elara welcome the visitor, old promises resurface, igniting new desires and unforeseen tensions. While Lord Blackwood honors a vow from the past, an unexpected play unfolds that may change their lives forever. But when an old enemy resurfaces, danger looms over their fragile peace. Can Asher uncover the truth, protect his family, and embrace the life he’s destined for before it all slips away?</p> <p>*<i>Blackwood Milk Farm</i> is for mature listeners. It includes mystery, intrigue, slice of life, and unconventional relationships.</p>"; 
